Fantastical v1.3.10
-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: http://flexibits.com/fantastical/


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "Fantastical v1.3.10.dmg" and Install the App.
- Open the Keygen app. First patch the app, then generate the necessary license/serial information. Enter (copy-paste) the generated information in the app.
- Enjoy.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update the app. You have been warned.
- If it says that the app is damaged. Then go to the System Preferences > Security and Privacy > General > Allow apps downloaded from and Select "Anywhere".
